Subject: #define HAVE_GAS_CFI_DIRECTIVE 0

This define may need to be zero to build with an older binutils;
binutils version 2.19.1 is my current goal.

---
 gcc/configure | 3 +--
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/gcc/configure b/gcc/configure
index 11dc1cc8603..1b963392679 100755
--- a/gcc/configure
+++ b/gcc/configure
@@ -22054,8 +22054,7 @@ fi
 
 
 cat >>confdefs.h <<_ACEOF
-#define HAVE_GAS_CFI_DIRECTIVE `if test $gcc_cv_as_cfi_directive = yes \
-       && test $gcc_cv_as_cfi_advance_working = yes; then echo 1; else echo 0; fi`
+#define HAVE_GAS_CFI_DIRECTIVE 0
 _ACEOF
 
 
